<tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-image">
<span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Frameless"><a href="/wiki/File:Balinski_pukelsheim_brams.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Balinski_pukelsheim_brams.jpg/250px-Balinski_pukelsheim_brams.jpg" decoding="async" width="250" height="188" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Balinski_pukelsheim_brams.jpg/500px-Balinski_pukelsheim_brams.jpg 1.5x" data-file-width="800" data-file-height="600"></a></span><div class="infobox-caption">From left: Michel Balinski, <a href="/w/index.php?title=Friedrich_Pukelsheim&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Friedrich Pukelsheim (page does not exist)">Friedrich Pukelsheim</a><span class="noprint" style="font-size:85%; font-style: normal;"> [<a href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Friedrich_Pukelsheim" class="extiw" title="de:Friedrich Pukelsheim">de</a>]</span>, <a href="/wiki/Steven_Brams" title="Steven Brams">Steven Brams</a>, Oberwolfach 2004</div>
</td></tr>
