<span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Michel_Balinski&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Articles"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span>
